long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Starknet Gas Price Tracker you need! All the info about the current gas price on Starknet and Ethereum is here.
This extension helps you keep track of the congestion on Starknet and Ethereum. It shows the latest fees to decide what's best for you to price your transactions.
